    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Infinite Library</strong> is a fast paced 2.5D Puzzle-Platformer. Play as Alex, a guardian of the Infinite Library. Your mission is to protect the library from imminent danger. Navigate through treacherous puzzles using ancient books that allow you to manipulate the laws of physics. Will you save the Library before it's too late?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078830/extras/18787af083857523856b63bbf7672e33.poster.avif?t=1728078259\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078830/extras/18787af083857523856b63bbf7672e33.webm?t=1728078259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078830/extras/18787af083857523856b63bbf7672e33.mp4?t=1728078259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Seven unique Levels</strong>: Navigate through seven unique floors where both your platforming skills and puzzle solving skills will be tested!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speed and Movement:</strong> Infinite Library allows the player to express themselves through many different movement options and abilities! Navigate the world by wavedashing, wall-jumping and so much more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenge Mode and Normal Mode</strong>: Play the game at your own pace with the choice between Challenge Mode and Normal Mode. Switch between the modes at any time to adapt the level to your liking!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Speedrun Friendly</strong>: Race against the clock with our standardized speedrun timer in challenge mode! Will you be the worlds speediest reader?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078830/extras/192a000f6cb98c8f4ff737c77cb892e2.avif?t=1728078259\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3078830/extras_big/192a000f6cb98c8f4ff737c77cb892e2.avif?t=1728078259 width=800 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hand Drawn Art</strong>: Enjoy the hand drawn art that can be found in cutscenes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Original Sound Track</strong>: Each level is accompanied by a song from our catchy original sound track!</p></li></ul>",
